ISLAMABAD, Oct 11 (APP): Sohail Nasir, former judge of Lahore High Court, has been appointed as Deputy Chairman while Syed Ihtesham Qadir Shah has been appointed Prosecutor General of the National Accountability Bureau (NAB).
A formal notification to this effect was issued by the Ministry of Law and Justice here Wednesday.
